<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(إِنَّمَا عوقبت عَن عَيْني ... فَاعْلَم يَا غُلَام)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>